---
title: Cherry-Glazed Beef Rump & Parmesan Roasted Veggies with Sautéed Cabbage
description: Round out the warmer months with this spectacular steak, drizzled with a sticky-sweet cherry glaze. And for the real
'cherry' on top, we’ve added Parmesan cheese to the roasted veggies and glowing sautéed cabbage depth of flavour to boot!
